Package servlets

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ServletAddNew
    ServletaddNew class is used to insert a new record into the vehicles database
    ServletDelete
    ServletDelete class is used to delete the vehicle record from the database
    ServletHome  
    ServletLogin
    ServletLogin class is allows the user to input username and password and login to the webapp
    ServletLogout
    ServletLogout allows the user to logout of the webapp and destroys session
    ServletShowSales
    ServletShowSales class displays all the records of sold vehicles in a table
    ServletSoldStatus
    ServletSoldStatus class is used to change the status of the vehicles sold and enter the sales records
    ServletUpdate
    ServletUpdate class is used to update the vehicle records in the database
